title: A < B < C < D < E < F < 50 A + B + C + D + E + F=91 All numbers are positive integers. What are A, B, C, D, E and F? - Quora

response.answer_text: There are multiple answers. For example 2+3+6+11+23+46 = 91. If you take 10 from 46 and redistributed 2 each you will have another solution like 4+5+8+13+25+36 = 91. You can also redistribute like 1+2+5+11+23+49. There are many other combinations
